comment: Harris (ORL) sets the screen on Allen (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Payton (ORL) makes contact with Conley's (MEM) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Conley (MEM) makes contact with Payton (ORL) that affects his RSBQ and driving shot attempt.
Gasol (MEM) obtains a legal guarding position as he defends Payton's (ORL) driving shot attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Payton.
Gasol (MEM) loses the ball and dislodges Oladipo (ORL) once the ball is loose.
Vucevic (ORL) legally contests Green's (MEM) driving dunk attempt.
Green (MEM) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Harris (ORL) that does not affect his FOM during the inbounds play.
RATR shows that Green (MEM) and Lee (MEM) maintain legal guarding position and cleanly strip the ball from Harris (ORL) who is inbounds when the ball makes contact with his leg.
Gasol (MEM) legally contests Vucevic's (ORL) jump shot attempt.
Allen (MEM) and Payton (ORL) make incidental contact with one another while chasing after the loose ball. Both players touch the ball simultaneously prior to it going OOB.
Green (MEM) and Harris (ORL) make incidental contact with one another away from the ball.
Gasol (MEM) sets the screen on Payton (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Oladipo (ORL) does not obtain a legal guarding position and makes contact with Conley's (MEM) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Conley (MEM) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Payton's (ORL) driving layup attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) obtains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact from Conley (MEM) as he contests the driving shot attempt.
R-SLA shows that Allen (MEM) dislodges Vucevic (ORL), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Gasol (MEM) sets the screen on Harris (ORL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Payton (ORL) makes body to body contact with Gasol (MEM), affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Harris (ORL) and Randolph (MEM) briefly engage and separate while looking to establish post position.
Oladipo (ORL) makes contact with Randolph's (MEM) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Vucevic (ORL) firms up as he sets the screen on Lee (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Randolph (MEM) is in a legal rebounding position and does not affect Harris' (ORL) ability to retrieve the rebound.
Payton (ORL) undercuts Randolph (MEM) after he secures the loose ball and causes him to fall to the floor.
RATR shows that Gasol (MEM) obtains a legal guarding position outside the restricted area and that he and Green (MEM) cleanly block Oladipo's (ORL) driving layup attempt.
Vucevic (ORL) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
Gasol (MEM) briefly engages with Vucevic (ORL) on the inbounds play.
Gasol (MEM) legally contests Fournier's (ORL) jump shot attempt and makes contact with the ball.
Fournier (ORL) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM) prior to the gather and shot attempt.
